      a(class="confirm-btn" href=`${linkLiteral}`) Verify Email
      p If that doesn't work then please copy and paste the link below into your browser instead:
      a(href=`${linkLiteral}`) #{linkLiteral}
      p(class="help-msg") If you need help or have any questions just reply to this email.


